{"tid":2217802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"芬蘭派「緝毒犬」檢測肺炎   準確度接近100%","createTime":"2020-09-25T17:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T17:25:38.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d433d8b5f64ec56816fcac2e0b8f83db29c2a5","tid":2217802,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2761776/【新冠肺炎】芬蘭派「緝毒犬」檢測%20準確度接近100-（多圖）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2761776%2F%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E8%8A%AC%E8%98%AD%E6%B4%BE%E3%80%8C%E7%B7%9D%E6%AF%92%E7%8A%AC%E3%80%8D%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%2520%E6%BA%96%E7%A2%BA%E5%BA%A6%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91100-%EF%BC%88%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96%EF%BC%89&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=00dfe8f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2761776/【新冠肺炎】芬蘭派「緝毒犬」檢測%20準確度接近100-（多圖）</a><br />\n<br />\n炎疫情持續，檢測工具一度缺貨，實驗室也瀕臨崩潰。芬蘭派出10隻「緝毒犬」到赫爾辛基機場作病毒檢測，透過嗅旅客的味道，判斷其是否染上新冠肺炎。研究顯示，偵測犬的準確度接近100%，遠勝目前流行的鼻咽及咽喉檢測。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2761776/0924_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2761776%2F0924_1024.jpg&h=a02a2362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n赫爾辛基大學獸醫學院一項研究發現，經訓練的狗可成功找出新冠肺炎患者，準確度接近100%。負責訓練偵測犬的Wise Nose派出10隻偵測犬到赫爾辛基機場，4隻偵測犬已開始「工作」。<br />\n<br />\n旅客入境時，需先用布擦拭皮膚，然後將布條放進杯子，交給當值的偵測犬，牠們會在另一個地方檢查樣品。如果樣本對檢測「呈陽性」，旅客會被轉送到機場的訊息站。<br />\n<br />\n由於今次是病毒檢測試驗計劃，旅客仍需接受常規的病毒檢測，以確保偵測犬的準確性。8歲大的Kossi是混種格雷伊獵犬，在7分鐘內學會了檢測病毒。<br />\n<br />\n芬蘭機場運營商Finavia表示，沒有其他機場如此大規模地使用偵測犬作病毒檢測，赫爾辛基機場是「先驅者」，可能「離擊退新冠肺炎又進一步」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，對於熱愛小動物的旅客而言，無疑是個壞消息。偵測犬上場的時候，不會與旅客有直接接觸，旅客亦要遵守「眼看手勿動」的規則。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2761776/groupphoto3_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2761776%2Fgroupphoto3_1024.jpg&h=d28393d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1f4f6bb6a86d73bbd909731f968351fba49ecd6","tid":2217802,"uid":2526,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T17:02:54.000Z","msg":"香港d狗淨係識599G"},{"pid":"49a43edb6edd16b5fada7a6aa1205fee91a41046","tid":2217802,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T17:04:00.000Z","msg":"狗仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85722a90fb00234151d10e00891699faf619ae0","tid":2217802,"uid":112241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T17:04:44.000Z","msg":"之前香港唔係有單狗中左武肺？ 隻狗完即棄？定再傳返出去？定個時香港鳩驗，根本對狗無作用？"},{"pid":"154ae56f78cee24cf61587adc614ef2c6d16c2a8","tid":2217802,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1f4f6bb6a86d73bbd909731f968351fba49ecd6","tid":2217802,"uid":2526,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T17:02:54.000Z","msg":"香港d狗淨係識599G"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T17:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15317a919438c12d38e8a4a6450ea3bcf628a853","tid":2217802,"uid":105207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T17:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad51220f7a29823f19212a5ead67f7c495825df3","tid":2217802,"uid":331949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1f4f6bb6a86d73bbd909731f968351fba49ecd6","tid":2217802,"uid":2526,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T17:02:54.000Z","msg":"香港d狗淨係識599G"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T17:07:34.000Z","msg":"限聚令！wou wou!"},{"pid":"d75f8d062ddcf87ed4ede17ef0e83f615f4ab204","tid":2217802,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi